Introduction

Gomak Boys was a South Korean project boy group under Kakao Entertainment. The group consists of five established soloists: Paul Kim, Melomance's Kim Min Seok, Jung Seung Hwan, Hoppipolla's Ha Hyunsang, and Big Naughty.
